FIG. 3 is an isometric view of a power inlet assembly for use in the power inlet arrangement of FIG. 2;


FIG. 4 is a partial front elevation view, with portions broken away, showing the lower portion of the power inlet assembly of FIG. 2; and


FIG. 5 is a partial section view taken along line 5--5 of FIG. 4.
